          "scid": "sn35.78:1.1",
          "pli": "“Yo kho, rādha, anattā tatra te chando pahātabbo. ",
          "en": "“Rādha, you should give up desire for what is not-self. …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.78:1.2",
