          "pli": "yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi anattā. Tatra te chando pahātabbo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.78:1.13",
          "pli": "Yo kho, rādha, anattā tatra te chando pahātabbo”ti. ",
